_______________________________________________________________________________
"Clairaudience"    
        This places a "presence" in a room.  The presence is like a
        monster which can neither attack nor be attacked and it will tell
        whatever it "hears"  to the psionicist.  Note:  the presence IS
        visible so it is not a means of invading privacy.
 
SP Cost:  30        Guild Level:  2     Potential Points:  1
 
Command:  clairaudience <target>  |  endaudience  (To end early)
